{"tid":1599440,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽]關於罷食","createTime":"2019-09-28T03:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T13:41:50.000Z","uid":214150,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c3373721882e50d7129d262b421b7e7214a23970","tid":1599440,"uid":214150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:39:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">重温一下黑心食品先</span></span></strong><br />\n地溝油，大頭奶粉<br />\n三聚氰胺，黑心染色饅頭<br />\n頭髮醬油，過期肉類<br />\n有毒白桃水果罐頭<br />\n<br />\n以上係咁多種類係結果，但最重要原因係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無良心</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">食品生產商，連鎖食店 最重要係良心</span></strong>[/size=5]<br />\n罷食唔止係因為佢無良心，係我地明白無良心，<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>[size=6]只向錢看既餐廳，為左錢係可以無視食客利益[/size=5]</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[size=6]罷食藍絲餐廳救港<br />\n同時係保護緊自己健康</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />文宣組幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfe20329684af952422ef222ebc6077bcb26b9f","tid":1599440,"uid":214150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:42:50.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"c1a0baee3d8a72600ad7160039704186048ccc8b","tid":1599440,"uid":214150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:43:06.000Z","msg":"1/10見"},{"pid":"a0aab9978faef180b260ad0b17f51aa89ba4647c","tid":1599440,"uid":214150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:43:22.000Z","msg":"28/9<br />\n29/9<br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"4be4c0e8b132742207fdcf1febe29a478835fedc","tid":1599440,"uid":200666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:44:27.000Z","msg":"文宣組"},{"pid":"06b2592b5c901e587aa81aea86d6ff4dce3aee99","tid":1599440,"uid":214150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T13:41:50.000Z","msg":"推啊"}]}